CDP 2023 C3.2

7.4 Task Force on ClimateRelated Financial Disclosures (TCFD)

We also apply different climate scenarios to assess physical climate-related risks and opportunities (see paragraph “Management of climate risks in our own operations”).

Our risk management approach to climate- related opportunities and risks Climate-related risks and opportunities are embedded in the

Siemens-wide ERM approach. All identified climate risks are assessed and measures for risk prevention, transfer, or miti- gation are devised for all relevant risks.